        "## 5. 損失函數\n",
        "\n",
        "使用組合損失函數：Dice Loss + Binary Cross Entropy"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": 25,
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
